Package: hud.gov
Title: HUD Department of Housing and Urban Development Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for HUD data including Fair Market Rents,
    Income Limits, Inspection Scores, Section 8 Contracts, and Homeless Counts.
    Includes LLM context injection via hud_context().
